title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table inside a grid cell
description: When attempting to export data from a table that is placed inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table inside a grid cell.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a table into one grid cell.
2. Insert another table into another grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data from either table.
